894.8, 567.3]}, {"text": "19,400", "bbox": [954.2, 546.5, 1011.5, 567.3]}, {"text": "Goodwill . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [287.5, 571.5, 894.8, 592.3]}, {"text": "80,285", "bbox": [954.2, 571.5, 1011.5, 592.3]}, {"text": "Deferred tax liabilities . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [287.5, 596.5, 894.8, 617.3]}, {"text": "(7,516)", "bbox": [957.6, 596.5, 1018.4, 617.3]}, {"text": "Other liabilities assumed . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [287.5, 621.5, 894.8, 642.3]}, {"text": "(8,497)", "bbox": [957.6, 621.5, 1018.4, 642.3]}, {"text": "$90,749", "bbox": [943.8, 654.8, 1011.5, 675.6]}, {"text": "The following were the identified intangible assets acquired and the respective estimated periods over which", "bbox": [204.2, 721.4, 1112.5, 742.2]}, {"text": "such assets will be amortized:", "bbox": [162.5, 746.4, 411.6, 767.2]}, {"text": "Amount", "bbox": [890.0, 828.4, 948.3, 845.1]}, {"text": "Weighted", "bbox": [1002.2, 795.1, 1070.7, 811.8]}, {"text": "Average", "bbox": [1006.8, 811.8, 1066.0, 828.4]}, {"text": "useful life", "bbox": [1002.0, 828.4, 1070.9, 845.1]}, {"text": "(In thousands)", "bbox": [867.6, 853.4, 970.8, 870.1]}, {"text": "(In years)", "bbox": [1002.0, 853.4, 1070.9, 870.1]}, {"text": "Completed technologies . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [204.2, 875.4, 836.4, 896.3]}, {"text": "$ 9,200", "bbox": [885.3, 875.4, 953.0, 896.3]}, {"text": "2.5", "bbox": [1023.4, 875.4, 1049.5, 896.3]}, {"text": "Customer relationships . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [204.2, 900.4, 836.4, 921.3]}, {"text": "4,300", "bbox": [906.1, 900.4, 953.0, 921.3]}, {"text": "4.1", "bbox": [1023.4, 900.4, 1049.5, 921.3]}, {"text": "Non-compete agreements . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [204.2, 925.4, 836.4, 946.3]}, {"text": "5,600", "bbox": [906.1, 925.4, 953.0, 946.3]}, {"text": "2.5", "bbox": [1023.4, 925.4, 1049.5, 946.3]}, {"text": "Trade names . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [204.2, 950.4, 836.4, 971.3]}, {"text": "300", "bbox": [921.8, 950.4, 953.0, 971.3]}, {"text": "1.5", "bbox": [1023.4, 950.4, 1049.5, 971.3]}, {"text": "Total . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [204.2, 983.8, 836.4, 1004.6]}, {"text": "$19,400", "bbox": [885.3, 983.8, 953.0, 1004.6]}, {"text": "In determining the purchase price allocation, the Company considered, among other factors, its intention to", "bbox": [204.2, 1050.3, 1112.5, 1071.2]}, {"text": "use the acquired assets and the historical and estimated future demand for acerno services. The fair value of", "bbox": [162.5, 1075.3, 1112.5, 1096.2]}, {"text": "intangible assets was based upon the income approach. In applying this approach, the values of the intangible", "bbox": [162.5, 1100.3, 1112.3, 1121.2]}, {"text": "assets acquired were determined using projections of revenues and expenses specifically attributed to the", "bbox": [162.5, 1125.3, 1112.4, 1146.2]}, {"text": "intangible assets. The income streams were then discounted to present value using estimated risk adjusted", "bbox": [162.5, 1150.3, 1112.4, 1171.2]}, {"text": "discount rates. The rate used to discount the expected future net cash flows from the intangible assets to their", "bbox": [162.5, 1175.3, 1112.4, 1196.2]}, {"text": "present values was based upon a weighted average cost of capital of 15%. The discount rate was determined after", "bbox": [162.5, 1200.3, 1112.3, 1221.2]}, {"text": "consideration of market rates of return on debt and equity capital, the weighted average return on invested capital", "bbox": [162.5, 1225.3, 1112.3, 1246.2]}, {"text": "and the risk associated with achieving forecasted sales related to the technology and assets acquired from acerno.", "bbox": [162.5, 1250.3, 1106.8, 1271.2]}, {"text": "The customer relationships were valued using the excess earnings method of income approach. The key", "bbox": [204.2, 1304.4, 1112.5, 1325.2]}, {"text": "assumptions used in valuing the customer relationships were as follows: discount rate of 15%, tax rate of 35%", "bbox": [162.5, 1329.4, 1112.5, 1350.2]}, {"text": "and estimated average economic life of seven years.", "bbox": [162.5, 1354.4, 597.2, 1375.2]}, {"text": "The relief-from-royalty method was used to value the completed technologies acquired from acerno. The", "bbox": [204.2, 1408.4, 1112.5, 1429.3]}, {"text": "relief-from-royalty method estimates the cost savings that accrue to the owner of an intangible asset that would", "bbox": [162.5, 1433.4, 1112.5, 1454.3]}, {"text": "63", "bbox": [627.1, 1484.1, 647.9, 1504.9]}]}